    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1641911076919-x200.jpg",
