            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>black beans</strong> and cook for a further 2 min or until the beans are warmed through – this is your <strong>Mexican-style beef</strong>,<strong> rice & beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1641911112460-x200.jpg",
