    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Mexican-style beef</strong>,<strong> rice & beans</strong> topped with a dollop of <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and the <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
